{
  "page": "Dornish Wars",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Dornish Wars</b> were the many conflicts fought after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>, between the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>. While the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a> was a full-fledged war that lasted for years, others were only raids or skirmishes.  \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Dornish_Wars\">The Dornish Wars</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dornish_Wars&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Dornish Wars\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Second_Dornish_War\" title=\"Second Dornish War\">Second Dornish War</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Third_Dornish_War\" title=\"Third Dornish War\">Third Dornish War</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fourth_Dornish_War\" title=\"Fourth Dornish War\">Fourth Dornish War</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Conquest_of_Dorne\" title=\"Conquest of Dorne\">Conquest of Dorne</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dornish_Wars&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Conques